---
// Views.astro — three ways to read the graph, with mini SVG diagrams.
---
<section id="views" class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-6 pt-[104px] sm:px-8">
  <div class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-teal-600">The graph</div>
  <h2 class="mt-3 text-[clamp(28px,5vw,38px)] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em]">One graph, three ways to read it.</h2>

  <div class="mt-11 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
    <!-- Topology -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-[14px] border border-ink-150 bg-white p-5">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 70" class="h-[58px] w-full">
        <line x1="56" y1="22" x2="120" y2="34" stroke="#11202e" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="120" y1="36" x2="170" y2="20" stroke="#0d9488" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="120" y1="40" x2="150" y2="58" stroke="#e0892a" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line>
        <circle cx="50" cy="20" r="7" fill="#3b6cf0"></circle>
        <circle cx="120" cy="37" r="8" fill="#0d9488"></circle>
        <circle cx="176" cy="18" r="6" fill="#0e9f8e"></circle>
        <rect x="142" y="52" width="13" height="11" rx="2" fill="#e0892a"></rect>
      </svg>
      <div class="mt-4 text-[19px] font-semibold">Topology</div>
      <p class="mt-[7px] text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-ink-500">Subgraphs with typed edges — calls, queries, publishes, contains, scales. Walk from a deployment to the endpoints it serves, the databases it queries, and the zones it runs in.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Flows -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-[14px] border border-ink-150 bg-white p-5">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 70" class="h-[58px] w-full">
        <rect x="6" y="28" width="40" height="16" rx="3" fill="#eef1f3" stroke="#dde4e9"></rect>
        <rect x="62" y="28" width="40" height="16" rx="3" fill="#eef1f3" stroke="#dde4e9"></rect>
        <rect x="118" y="28" width="40" height="16" rx="3" fill="#f0faf8" stroke="#0d9488"></rect>
        <line x1="46" y1="36" x2="62" y2="36" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="102" y1="36" x2="118" y2="36" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="158" y1="36" x2="172" y2="36" stroke="#0d9488" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
      </svg>
      <div class="mt-4 text-[19px] font-semibold">Flows</div>
      <p class="mt-[7px] text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-ink-500">Canonical request shapes collapsed from many traces — retries, fan-out, and sibling order normalized away. Each flow is a pipeline of hops with the component, operation, and the db or topic it touches.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Reliability -->
    <div class="flex flex-col rounded-[14px] border border-ink-150 bg-white p-5">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 70" class="h-[58px] w-full">
        <line x1="100" y1="35" x2="40" y2="16" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="100" y1="35" x2="40" y2="54" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="100" y1="35" x2="160" y2="18" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <line x1="100" y1="35" x2="162" y2="52" stroke="#aeb8c2" stroke-width="1.6"></line>
        <circle cx="40" cy="16" r="5" fill="#aeb8c2"></circle>
        <circle cx="40" cy="54" r="5" fill="#aeb8c2"></circle>
        <circle cx="160" cy="18" r="5" fill="#aeb8c2"></circle>
        <circle cx="162" cy="52" r="5" fill="#aeb8c2"></circle>
        <circle cx="100" cy="35" r="9" fill="#e0892a"></circle>
      </svg>
      <div class="mt-4 text-[19px] font-semibold">Reliability</div>
      <p class="mt-[7px] text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-ink-500">Structural risks become queries — single points of failure, large fan-outs, cyclical dependencies, blast radius, and dead (uncalled) endpoints. Ask them over REST, or let Claude find them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
